node.text: Two weeks ago we went on the Run To Ibiza with our friends at Roger Dubuis: 1400+ km of driving the Aventador S in a supercar convoy through Portugal and Spain, ending up in Ibiza for closing weekend. Here is a quick 1 minute recap of an unforgettable trip.
